quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"Mutabani wa Mariam (Issa) bwe yakubirwako ekifaananyi, ogenda okulaba nga abantu bo kibawogganya (olwessanyu)"
  43,58,"Nebagamba nti abaffe ba katonda baffe bebasinga oba yye, tebakukubira kifaananyi ekyo okugyako lwa kuwalaaza mpaka, nedda (si ekyo kyokka kye bawakanya) bulijjo bo bantu bawakanyi"
  43,59,"(Isa) tali yye okugyako okuba nti muddu waffe nga abalala, twamugabira ekyengera (kyo bwa Nabbi) era netumufuula ekyokulabirako eri abaaana ba Israil"
  43,60,Singa twayagala abamu mu mmwe twandibafudde ba Malayika nga basikiragana mu nsi
  43,61,"Era mazima yye (Isa) kabonero akaliranga okusembera kw'olunaku lw'enkomerero, n'olwekyo temukibuusabusaamu naakamu era mungoberere, lino lye kkubo eggolokofu"
  43,62,Era Sitane tabasuuliranga emisanvu (mu kkubo) anti mazima yye ku mmwe mulabe owolwatu
  43,63,(Nabbi) Isa bweyajja nobunnyonnyofu yagamba nti mazima mbajjidde nebigambo ebyamagezi era mbannyonnyole ebimu kwebyo bye muwakanamu kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  43,64,"Mazima Katonda ye Mukama omulabirizi wange era Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, kale mumusinze lino lye kkubo eggolokofu"
  43,65,Wabula ebibiina byayawukana nga biva mu bo bennyini (ku nsonga ya Isa) kale okubonabona okwe bibonyobonyo by'olunaku oluzito kugenda kubeera kwabo abeeyisa obubi
  43,66,Abaffe (balina kye) balindirira okugyako ekiseera eky'enkomerero okuba nga kibajjira ekibwatukira nga nabo tebamanyi
  43,67,"Abomukwano ku lunaku olwo, abamu baliba balabe ba bannabwe okugyako abatya Katonda"